title: Omsom Saucy Noodles Bundle Proud, loud Asian flavors in 6 minutes or less! | 4 Servings
description: Omsom was started by two sisters (daughters of Vietnamese refugees); its mission is to reclaim and celebrate Asian American flavors with a whole lot of flair. These two noodle-based dishes bring restaurant-quality Asian staples right to your kitchen. The Coconut Lemongrass Curry Saucy Noodles, with a luscious and aromatic coconut curry sauce, are an homage to Thai khao soi. The Soy Garlic Saucy Noodles, with their bold, umami-forward sauce, are a nod to Chinese sizzling oil noodles. Get creative and top the noodles with cooked chicken, a fried egg, or a sprinkle of fresh cilantro (additional ingredients not included)!

